QuestData.Title: Never Outgunned
QuestData.Description:
This is our new home now, and we will fight to keep it!
We may be outnumbered here, but we aren't going to be outgunned.
Find us every axe, sword, spear, crossbow, and gun for our rebellion!
QuestData.CompletionText: We'll need more than that. Find us some weapons!
